1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 2=

21
00:01:23,950 --> 00:01:25,480
Do you know who the killer is?

22
00:01:26,710 --> 00:01:27,590
I don't.

23
00:01:27,590 --> 00:01:28,430
I do.

24
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,000
The killer

25
00:01:30,150 --> 00:01:31,790
is you.

26
00:01:34,210 --> 00:01:35,050
You…

27
00:01:35,070 --> 00:01:36,150
I saw everything.

28
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:40,230
How you lured Qiu Yu to the rockery,

29
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:42,040
how you set the trap,

30
00:01:42,070 --> 00:01:43,430
and how you acted

31
00:01:43,430 --> 00:01:44,270
all panicked

32
00:01:44,370 --> 00:01:45,320
after you pulled it off.

33
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:46,920
I saw it all.

34
00:01:47,310 --> 00:01:48,590
You're the murderer.

35
00:01:48,590 --> 00:01:50,430
Why am I the one who has to die?

36
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,520
I...

37
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,040
I'm sorry.

38
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,400
I had no choice.

39
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,430
No choice?

40
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:02,960
Let's hear it.

41
00:02:06,350 --> 00:02:08,000
She found out about my true identity

42
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:09,800
and used it to blackmailed me.

43
00:02:10,910 --> 00:02:12,150
I had to kill her.

44
00:02:13,910 --> 00:02:16,000
I didn't know you'd get dragged into this.

45
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:16,840
If I had known…

46
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,750
It's not too late.

47
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:23,470
Don't just say you're sorry.

48
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,470
You still have a chance to fix this.

49
00:02:31,710 --> 00:02:33,430
I'll find a way to get you out.

50
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,630
Lady Zhi Hui,

51
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:36,590
it's late.

52
00:02:36,590 --> 00:02:37,870
You should head back.

53
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:41,190
If you really want to save me,

54
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,710
go tell everyone the truth.

55
00:02:42,710 --> 00:02:44,190
Admit that you are the real killer.

56
00:02:44,190 --> 00:02:45,030
Go.

57
00:02:47,430 --> 00:02:48,560
I'm so sorry.

58
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:50,030
I'll do everything I can to save you.

59
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:54,630
Wait, Zhi Hui.

60
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,120
Zhi Hui, come back.

61
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:01,960
If I die,

62
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,630
I'll haunt you forever.

63
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:04,680
Step back.

64
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,800
Your Majesty.

65
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,240
Your Majesty,

66
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,560
how is the Empress Dowager?

67
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:23,630
I've been praying

68
00:03:23,630 --> 00:03:25,400
for her recovery every day.

69
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,960
What are you doing here?

70
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,470
We were worried about Her Majesty,

71
00:03:29,750 --> 00:03:31,000
so we came to help tend to her.

72
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,800
She needs peace and quiet.

73
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:33,960
No disturbances.

74
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,560
If you actually care about her,

75
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,030
stop coming here to cause a scene.

76
00:03:37,030 --> 00:03:38,520
Wait until she's better.

77
00:03:38,750 --> 00:03:39,590
Your Majesty,

78
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,630
I recently found a treasure.

79
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,560
A work from the golden years,

80
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:46,120
said to be painted
by Her Majesty as a child.

81
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:48,280
Seeing it might

82
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:50,430
soothe her mind while she's ill.

83
00:03:54,410 --> 00:03:55,710
Sixi, get the Imperial Physician.

84
00:03:55,910 --> 00:03:57,560
Go get the physician.

85
00:03:59,030 --> 00:03:59,960
Your Majesty,

86
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:01,560
no need.

87
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:04,430
The baby is kicking me.

88
00:04:06,910 --> 00:04:07,750
Your Majesty.

89
00:04:10,190 --> 00:04:11,560
He's kicking again.

90
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,960
Feel it.

91
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:16,270
He's so restless.

92
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:18,120
He must miss his father.

93
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:20,560
You should come visit us more often.

94
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,200
Fine.

95
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:24,270
I'll go back to your palace with you

96
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:26,310
to calm

97
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,350
the little one down.

98
00:04:27,390 --> 00:04:28,230
Mm.

99
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,650
Your Majesty,

100
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:30,560
that painting...

101
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:33,360
I went through the storehouse to find it.

102
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,510
You haven't looked at it.

103
00:04:34,510 --> 00:04:36,000
I'm going to Consort Duan's.

104
00:04:36,430 --> 00:04:37,950
I'll catch up with you another day.

105
00:04:41,510 --> 00:04:42,350
Your Majesty.

106
00:04:55,950 --> 00:04:56,870
Die.

107
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,310
Live.

108
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,040
Die.

109
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,000
Live.

110
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,360
Die.

111
00:05:15,070 --> 00:05:17,190
If I die,

112
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:19,800
maybe I can go home?

113
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,680
No way.

114
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:31,830
That'd hurt too much.

115
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,720
Maid Ye Jin.

116
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:42,560
Come out.

117
00:05:44,380 --> 00:05:51,860
(Department of Justice)

118
00:05:51,870 --> 00:05:52,710
Let's go.

119
00:05:53,130 --> 00:05:54,560
Someone important wants to see you.

120
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:56,800
Who is it?

121
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,310
You'll know when we get there.

122
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,560
You sure talk a lot.

123
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,600
So mysterious.

124
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:06,950
Is this good luck or bad?

125
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,830
Go on. Inside.

126
00:06:15,830 --> 00:06:16,670
Mm.

127
00:06:37,950 --> 00:06:39,310
I am Ye Jin.

128
00:06:39,310 --> 00:06:40,510
Greetings, Your Excellency.

129
00:06:40,870 --> 00:06:42,160
Ye Jin,

130
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,800
if you can diagnose the illness,

131
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:46,310
you'll be spared.

132
00:06:48,630 --> 00:06:51,360
(Only the 14th Prince knows
I can practice medicine.)

133
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:52,630
(The one behind this today)

134
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:54,120
(must be him.)

135
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:56,630
(But I don't know who the patient is.)

136
00:07:09,430 --> 00:07:10,830
(Defined joints.)

137
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:12,040
(Not a woman's hand.)

138
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:14,000
(The patient is a man.)

139
00:07:16,510 --> 00:07:19,360
(Calluses on the palm.)

140
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,680
(He's trained in martial arts.)

141
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:27,240
(Marks from wearing an archer's ring.)

142
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:29,070
(This man's of high status.)

143
00:07:29,070 --> 00:07:30,430
(Could it be…)

144
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:35,800
The owner of this hand is physically strong,

145
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,190
but has a hidden condition.

146
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:39,240
If it's not treated,

147
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,240
he likely

148
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,270
won't live past 20.

149
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,630
How dare you?

150
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:47,190
You're talking nonsense.

151
00:07:47,830 --> 00:07:50,750
Ignoring illness is a grave mistake.

152
00:07:53,630 --> 00:07:55,040
Your Excellency behind the curtain.

153
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:57,160
You're gifted and perceptive,

154
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:58,600
but you overthink.

155
00:07:59,390 --> 00:08:00,830
You can see your own fate,

156
00:08:00,870 --> 00:08:02,160
yet feel powerless to change it.

157
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,160
Over time,

158
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:05,000
that's turned into a condition of the mind.

159
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,160
You also suffer from insomnia

160
00:08:07,190 --> 00:08:08,950
and have trouble falling asleep.

161
00:08:09,390 --> 00:08:11,310
When you finally do,

162
00:08:11,310 --> 00:08:12,630
the nightmares come.

163
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,040
And headaches too.

164
00:08:14,950 --> 00:08:16,000
Am I right?

165
00:08:26,190 --> 00:08:27,430
Then according to you,

166
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,440
what exactly

167
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,640
should I do?

168
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:34,240
Keep me, the miracle doctor,

169
00:08:34,630 --> 00:08:36,000
by your side to treat you.

170
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:38,030
How dare you flirt with the Prince?

171
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:43,390
You've got some skill.

172
00:08:44,150 --> 00:08:46,200
You said you could
cure the Empress Dowager.

173
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,600
How sure are you?

174
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,320
One hundred percent.

175
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:51,120
Give me one month.

176
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:53,390
I guarantee her health will improve.

177
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:54,960
Fine.

178
00:08:55,510 --> 00:08:57,750
I'll give you one month.

179
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,390
Cure her,

180
00:08:59,630 --> 00:09:01,790
and I'll spare your life.

181
00:09:03,390 --> 00:09:04,240
No problem.

182
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,750
I'll head back and get my things.

183
00:09:05,750 --> 00:09:07,150
Then I'll report to Cining Palace.

184
00:09:13,500 --> 00:09:14,360
Your Highness,

185
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,550
do you really trust her?

186
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,000
She looks like

187
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:19,510
a total fraud to me.

188
00:09:19,510 --> 00:09:20,750
I'm just desperate for a cure.

189
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,080
Regardless,

190
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,750
if there's a shred of hope,

191
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:27,390
I'm willing to try it for my mother.

192
00:09:27,910 --> 00:09:29,120
But Consort Lan

193
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:31,670
might be a problem.

194
00:09:31,790 --> 00:09:34,120
She's the one who solved the murder case

195
00:09:34,550 --> 00:09:37,000
and caught the killer. This might…

196
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,320
Offended or not.

197
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:39,750
It has nothing

198
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,390
to do with me.

199
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:49,080
Didn't expect

200
00:09:49,630 --> 00:09:51,790
to get close to my idol like that.

201
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:54,030
Okay, it's not really him,

202
00:09:54,390 --> 00:09:56,200
but he looks exactly the same.

203
00:09:56,390 --> 00:09:57,720
Close enough. I'll take it.

204
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,870
This transmigration is totally worth it.

205
00:10:02,910 --> 00:10:05,600
I come from a family of traditional doctors,

206
00:10:05,870 --> 00:10:07,910
I've got modern medical knowledge,

207
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:10,200
and I know the plot inside out.

208
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:13,390
With just a few easy moves,

209
00:10:14,910 --> 00:10:16,750
I can rewrite my fate,

210
00:10:16,750 --> 00:10:19,790
and settle into palace life
without breaking a sweat.

211
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:22,390
With cheats like this,

212
00:10:22,390 --> 00:10:24,150
I'm basically the chosen one.

213
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,670
And if I can have

214
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:30,080
an epic romance with An Jingyu,

215
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,440
my life will be complete.

216
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:38,870
♪I am but an outsider♪

217
00:10:38,890 --> 00:10:41,080
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

218
00:10:41,300 --> 00:10:45,340
♪Outwit the world but not the way we meet♪

219
00:10:45,340 --> 00:10:49,580
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

220
00:10:53,860 --> 00:10:57,110
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

221
00:10:57,280 --> 00:11:00,670
♪In a world of lies, you're all that's clear♪

222
00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:03,180
♪I know how this story ends♪

223
00:11:03,180 --> 00:11:07,750
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

224
00:11:08,050 --> 00:11:12,190
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

225
00:11:17,140 --> 00:11:20,450
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

226
00:11:20,450 --> 00:11:23,730
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

227
00:11:23,930 --> 00:11:27,010
♪A history that no one can search♪

228
00:11:27,280 --> 00:11:30,540
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

229
00:11:30,590 --> 00:11:32,340
♪I am but an outsider♪

230
00:11:32,340 --> 00:11:34,580
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

231
00:11:34,580 --> 00:11:38,640
♪Outwit the world but not the way we meet♪

232
00:11:38,640 --> 00:11:43,290
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

233
00:11:47,220 --> 00:11:50,620
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

234
00:11:50,620 --> 00:11:53,980
♪In a world of lies, you're all that's clear♪

235
00:11:53,980 --> 00:11:56,450
♪I know how this story ends♪

236
00:11:56,450 --> 00:12:00,640
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

237
00:12:00,640 --> 00:12:03,910
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

238
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:07,700
♪Please forget me and move on♪

239
00:12:07,700 --> 00:12:13,940
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

240
00:12:17,100 --> 00:12:25,460
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

241
00:12:29,030 --> 00:12:38,750
♪When do I finally wake♪
